text: Pine Valley (Provo River), is a valley along the North Fork of the Provo River in Summit and Wasatch counties in north or north-central Utah, United States. The former Stewart Ranch, which includes five buildings listed on the National Register of Historic Places, runs along it. ==References== Category:Landforms of Summit County, Utah Category:Landforms of Wasatch County, Utah Category:Valleys of Utah
